	    an ideal defining the conormal variety in $\PP^n \times (\PP^n)^*$.
    Description 
    	Text
	    For a complex projective variety $X=V(I)\subset \PP^n$ this command computes the ideal of the conormal variety $Con(X)$ in $\PP^n \times (\PP^n)^*$.
	Example 
